{
  "stem": "18575.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After you came to camp, they kill you, because you committed sabotage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you'd be very careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And did a-- a decent job, they left you alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The master that I had, the German master, his name was Miller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a decent man-- at least he looked like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In fact, I was sick once there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I, again, had temperature, and he saw it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were cells with doors with high voltage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were high voltage rails running the whole ceilings, like 10,000, 20,000 volts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on that door was a dead head with two bones and 'Warning-- do not open,' you know, 'dangerous.' He used to open the cell, and tell me, lay down on the bottom, and close the cell.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS would never get near it, OK?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So he let me rest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- and in compared to Majdanek was incomparable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because for once, we had-- even though the banks-- lost my [INAUDIBLE]-- the bunks in the-- in the barracks were three bunks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had individual bunk for yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were-- you got the, three times, food a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, we smuggled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We smuggled things from the camp to the ward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were Polish workers, civilian workers.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
